DOWNLOAD WATERMARK FREE: http://www.naturerelaxation.com/products/golden-echoes-of-nature-short-2-minute-relaxing-4k-music-video
"The call of Nature echoes in all of us, we need only make time to listen."  This video features some spectacular healing aspen forest scenes filmed in Kings Canyon National Park, paired with a custom written track by talented music composer Travis Revell.  A bit sad, yet uplifting, it is a great way to slow down for just a few minutes and reflect on the importance of Nature in our world today.
MORE INFO:
Music: "Echoes" by Travis Revell
Video from the 90 minute 4K video "Golden Forest Relaxation" @ http://youtu.be/Q4OWU2iZPJw
